{"tid":1023583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典外交部長：對駐華大使林戴安行為“非常憤怒”","createTime":"2019-02-16T01:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:52:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"59c41a1360a4fd981209dc203de95540d496edf1","tid":1023583,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/F25A2036-1BBF-44E5-9259-2D65D4815405_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FF25A2036-1BBF-44E5-9259-2D65D4815405_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=e636dccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑞典外長瓦爾斯特倫（2018年3月16 路透社）<br />\n<br />\n瑞典外交部長瓦爾斯特倫星期五表示，她對瑞典駐華大使安排桂民海的女兒Angela Gui同兩名商人會面感到&ldquo;非常憤怒&rdquo;。據稱這兩名商人在會面中曾經威脅桂民海的女兒。<br />\n<br />\n瓦爾斯特倫在瑞典公共電台節目中說，瑞典外交部事先不知道駐華大使林戴安安排的斯德哥爾摩的會面。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典駐華大使林戴安已經被召回國，接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n香港前銅鑼灣書店出版商桂民海的女兒星期三說，瑞典駐華大使林戴安今年1月25日在斯德哥爾摩為她安排了一次跟兩名商人的&ldquo;奇怪&rdquo;會面。她說，他們在主動提出要幫助她父親桂民海獲釋後，曾經威脅她不要對任何人談起這場秘密會面，並在未來的一段時間裡保持低調。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典公民桂民海曾經是香港銅鑼灣書店的出版商， 因為出版一些政治敏感的書籍，2015年10月在泰國神秘失踪。在國際社會強烈反應下，桂民海出現在中國官方電視上&ldquo;認罪&rdquo;，隨後被關押兩年。<br />\n<br />\n桂民海今年54歲，2017年10月從拘留所獲釋，但後來又失踪。去年1月桂民海的女兒說，桂民海在乘坐開往北京的火車上被中國公安帶走。當時兩名瑞典外交官在場。中國後來證實拘留了桂民海。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/sweden-china-gui-minhai-ambassador-20190215/4788512.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fsweden-china-gui-minhai-ambassador-20190215%2F4788512.html&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=3a3d687b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/sweden-china-gui-minhai-ambassador-20190215/4788512.html</a>"},{"pid":"cc64480ff89ad62bcc5678f9ba8b549bc04ddd3d","tid":1023583,"uid":121146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"德國人表示中國比美國友善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6416d3a5a6b547c21ac433c8596ce135856214b8","tid":1023583,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"好彩佢個女無俾人融左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e3ea894ee497c695413de53eefb2cf5533bacb","tid":1023583,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"歐豬國駐華大使 10個有9個變內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2546551e0dd65781600da7d4ac2b767da606a7","tid":1023583,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253107137f9df35732a5e3130cdc2d4ffef47c00","tid":1023583,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"駐支那 就比大醬缸污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07954b971de996ec8e38a2012b21e990c8bba330","tid":1023583,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯桂民海係大使"},{"pid":"880012f07f308b1e25791bcd15fce1aa86843f4f","tid":1023583,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29e3ea894ee497c695413de53eefb2cf5533bacb","tid":1023583,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"歐豬國駐華大使 10個有9個變內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:32:35.000Z","msg":"歐豬根本就係on9<br />\n應該要加插人手監視d駐華大使"},{"pid":"6ceb48253302393dbeadea2075c7d068bd134c2a","tid":1023583,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"瑞典婆同強力部門合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=